summary: Made a breton and thought she looked pretty.
descriptionHtml:
She\'s tanned enough to look like a redguard, but she\'s really a breton without a wrinkly forehead.  I put her up because I liked what I saw when I was finished.  YMMV.

Save game is about 5 seconds after stepping off the prisoner wagon.

Screenshots taken using \"Male and Female Press Out the Wrinkles n Forehead v3\" at http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=139
author: Insufferable Smartypants
